  "title": "IT Executive / IT Network & System Support ( Woodalnds )",
  "description": "<p><strong>1. IT Infrastructure Support</strong></p>\n<p>· Maintain and troubleshoot <strong>hardware</strong> (PCs, printers, barcode scanners, etc.)</p>\n<p>· Support <strong>network infrastructure</strong>: LAN/WAN, switches, routers, Wi-Fi</p>\n<p>· Ensure <strong>servers</strong> and <strong>data storage</strong> are running smoothly (file servers, domain controllers)</p>\n<p><strong>2. System Administration</strong></p>\n<p>· Manage <strong>user accounts</strong>, email, Active Directory, file permissions</p>\n<p>· Monitor <strong>IT security</strong> (antivirus, firewalls, data protection policies)</p>\n<p>· Perform <strong>regular backups</strong> and ensure disaster recovery plans are in place</p>\n<p><strong>3. Manufacturing/Production System Support</strong></p>\n<p>· Provide technical support for <strong>MES (Manufacturing Execution Systems)</strong>, ERP, or factory-specific systems</p>\n<p><u><strong>Requirement</strong></u></p>\n<p>· <strong>Diploma or Degree</strong> in Information Technology, Computer Science, Engineering, or related field</p>\n<p>· <strong>1–3 years</strong> of experience in IT support, networking, or systems administration</p>\n<p>· Experience in a <strong>manufacturing or factory environment</strong> is a <strong>plus</strong></p>\n<p>Good Pay + Good allowance + Good Bonus</p>\n<p>Interested candidates please send an updated Resume / CV in Ms Word format to lilian@recruitflash.com or WhatsApp’s your resume to 98332779 ( no Calls)</p>\n<p>Consultant in-charge : Quah Li Lian (Lilian) ( Registration No: R1983286 )</p>",
